Class RepositoryContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • RepositoryContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModelController, IModelView, IObservable

    public class RepositoryContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements IModelView, IModelController
    The RepositoryContainer provides a facade for the model and exposes the methods required by the view and the controller.
